Prof. Subhash C. Yaragal Assumes Role as Deputy Director at NITK Surathkal. 

Dr. Subhash C. Yaragal has taken charge as the Deputy Director of the National Institute of Technology Karnataka (NITK), Surathkal. on 01.08.2024. A renowned academic and experienced administrator, Prof. Yaragal's new role is a notable addition to the institute's leadership.

Joining NITK Surathkal in 1996, Prof. Yaragal has played a pivotal role in the institute's growth and development. Over the years, he has held several key administrative positions, including Member of the Board of Governors, Dean (Planning & Development), and Head of the Department of Civil Engineering.

Prof. Yaragal's educational background is rooted in NITK Surathkal, where he completed his Bachelor‚Äôs in Civil Engineering in the year 1987. He pursued higher education at the Indian Institute of Science (IISc) Bangalore, earning his Master's and Doctoral degrees. The director, functionaries, staff and the entire NITK Family extended a heartfelt congratulations to Prof. Yaragal on his esteemed¬†appointment.

