On the 21st and 22nd of March 2023, the Ministry of MSME will host a two-day National Workshop on Design Components in partnership with the Centre for System Design, NITK Surathkal, and MSME DFO Mangalore at NITK. 

The workshop's primary goal is to bring together the Indian manufacturing sector and the Design expertise/Design fraternity to give expert advise and cost-effective solutions on real-time design challenges for new product creation, continuous improvement, and value addition in existing/new goods. This Design Scheme will assist MSMEs in obtaining advise on all elements of design and achieving their design-related objectives with the assistance of professional designers.Wipro 3D, Lucid engineering, graduates of NID, Ahmedabad, and NITK, as well as successful MSMEs, will provide lectures and demonstrations. The session is completely free to attend. You can register both online and on the spot. 

